OOC: Jason, do not ignore my attacks on Angel Prime.  Cyclonus and Scoruge 
each fired a high powered laser blast at you

:::The Destrocons/Falcon/Snare/Cyclonus/Scourge:::

::All of my Destrons are upset, now that their leader is gone, but they hope 
that these bots will join them to keep the Destrons alive::
Ramjet: Base? We are Destrons, we have been in the Destron base through our 
entire careers as Destrons.  We served under Magmatron, Bobertron, Shredder, 
and Magmatron again. But that is beside the point. Together we will keep the 
Destrons alive until Magmatron and the others return.

--part1_d1.33c1c56.27d5b20f_boundary
